remarks: A cardinal strictly dominates its members.  Equivalent to Proposition 10.37 of [TakeutiZaring] p. 93.  (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 15-Jan-2013.)  (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 4-Jun-2015.)
statement: cardsdomel $p |- ( ( A e. On /\ B e. dom card ) -> ( A ~< B <-> A e. ( card ` B ) ) ) $.
